title: User query: Plan description from client LLM
log: Create a plan that summarizes all line items shipped before a cutoff date, defined as July 1st 1998 minus 90 days. The query must group the results by return flag and line status. For each group, calculate the total quantity, total extended price, average quantity, average extended price, and the number of rows. You don't need ordering or sortineg. The output must be in textfile.

operations.table: (SELECT l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_shipdate FROM lineitem) as X

operations.udf: (r: org.apache.wayang.basic.data.Record) => { val ret = r.getField(0).toString; val lin = r.getField(1).toString; val qty = r.getField(2).asInstanceOf[Int]; val ext = r.getField(3).asInstanceOf[Double]; ((ret, lin), (qty, ext, 1)) }

(a: ((String, String), (Int, Double, Int)), b: ((String, String), (Int, Double, Int))) => { val k = a._1; val aq = a._2._1 + b._2._1; val ae = a._2._2 + b._2._2; val ac = a._2._3 + b._2._3; (k, (aq, ae, ac)) }

(t: ((String, String), (Int, Double, Int))) => { val key = t._1; val qty = t._2._1; val ext = t._2._2; val cnt = t._2._3; val avgQty = if (cnt != 0) qty.toDouble / cnt else 0.0; val avgExt = if (cnt != 0) ext.toDouble / cnt else 0.0; (key._1, key._2, qty, ext, avgQty, avgExt, cnt) }

log.thoughts: Load lineitem, filter by ship date before 1998-04-03, then aggregate by (l_returnflag, l_linestatus) to compute totals and averages, finally write the grouped summary to a text file.

title: Class: PlanMapper Mapped plan finalized for execution

data.table: (SELECT l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_shipdate FROM (SELECT l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_shipdate FROM lineitem) as X) as X

data.udf: (r: org.apache.wayang.basic.data.Record) => { val ret = r.getField(0).toString; val lin = r.getField(1).toString; val qty = r.getField(2).asInstanceOf[Int]; val ext = r.getField(3).asInstanceOf[Double]; ((ret, lin), (qty, ext, 1)) }

(a: ((String, String), (Int, Double, Int)), b: ((String, String), (Int, Double, Int))) => { val k = a._1; val aq = a._2._1 + b._2._1; val ae = a._2._2 + b._2._2; val ac = a._2._3 + b._2._3; (k, (aq, ae, ac)) }

(t: ((String, String), (Int, Double, Int))) => { val key = t._1; val qty = t._2._1; val ext = t._2._2; val cnt = t._2._3; val avgQty = if (cnt != 0) qty.toDouble / cnt else 0.0; val avgExt = if (cnt != 0) ext.toDouble / cnt else 0.0; (key._1, key._2, qty, ext, avgQty, avgExt, cnt) }
